    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Manneem Kalpeem buhs\ntohs no ta Eihbanus nowest Juhr-\nMallâ / un es weddichn tohs\neekſch Plohſteem pahr Juheru us\nto Weetu / fo tu man finnainu\ndarrifi / un es atraisifchnu tohs\ntur/ ka tu tohs warr nowest. Tu\ndarrifi arri mannu Prahtu / un\ndohfi Barribu preekſch mannu\nNammu."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tä dewe Jrains Sala-\nmanam Zeedru-Kohkus un Pree-\ndes/ ka wiꞥſch pats gribbeja."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Salamanß dewe Jrain-\nmann divideſmits tuhkſtoſchus\nKorus Kweeschu par Barribu\npreekſch winna Nammut / un di-\nwideſmits Korus faqruhſtas Et-\njes. To dewe Salamanß Jrain-\nmann tkgadduß."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS dewe\nSalamaxam Gudribu/ ittin ka\ntas tam bij runnajs. Un starp\nJrainu un Salamann bija\nMeers/ un tee darrija abbi diwi\nweenu Derribu."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas kehnifsch Sala-\nmanß islaſſiia weenu Pulku no\nwiﬀa Jraëka/ un tas islaſſihts\nPulks bija trihsdefinits tuhkſto-\nschi Wihrf."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fuhttija tohs\nus to Libbanu / definits tuhkſto-\nschus weenâ Mehnefi pa Pul-\nkeem : Weenu Mehnefi bija tee\nus Libbanu/un diwi Mehneschus\nbija tee Mahjäs/ un Adonirams\nbija pahr fcho islaſſitu Pulku."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Salamanam biʃ arr-\nfeptindefinits tuhkſtoschi Nastu-\nNeffeji / un aſtondefinits tuhk-\nstoschi Zirteji us to Kalnu."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bes teem Pawaldneekem\nSalamana/ kas pahr fcho Dar-\nbu eeżeli/ to bija trihs tuhkſto-\nschi un trihsſiunts/ kas tohs Lan-\ndis peeluhkoja/ kas to Darbu pa-\ndarrija."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas kehnifsch paweh-\nleja/ ka bij atwest leelus Akmi-\nnus/ dahrgus Akminus/ apzir-\nſtus Akminus/ tam Namman\nto Grunti lift."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Salamanam Reimne-\nschi/ un Jrainam Reimneſchi/ un\ntee Gibliteri apzirte tohs/ un va-\nfaifija tohs Kohkus/ un tohs Ak-\nmiuns/ par ta Namma Uſtaifſi-\nſchanu."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta VI. Nodalla.\nPreekſch-Sihme / Gazrums un Augſtums ta\nDeewa Namma: 2. Ta Pagalmja: 3. Dee-\nwa Apfohlſchana: 11/ 12. Wiſs tas Deewa Namß tohp eekſch feptineem Gadbeem\npabeigts: 37.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notiffahß zettor-\netä fimtä un aſtotä definits mitä Gaddä pehz to Jrainäka Behrun Iseeſchanas no\nEgiptes-Geimmes/zettortä Gaddä tahs Waldiſchanas Salamanä/ tai Mehnefi Siw/ (ſchis irr tas ohtrs Mehnes)/ tad uſtat-\nfija wiꞥſch ta KUNGA Namm."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Namm/ fo tas kehnifsch Salamanß tam KUNGAM darrija/ bija feſchdefinits Ohlekſchu Gazruma / un diwi-\nDefinits"
    }
  ],
